  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Planar Adventures pg. 46</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate illusion <strong>CL</strong> 11th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> none; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3><em>Shadow blending</em> armor is drab and mutes any colors in its wearer's attire into dull grays. Attacks against the wearer in dim light have a 40% miss chance instead of the normal 20%. This ability does not grant total concealment; it only increases the miss chance. If the armor also has the <em>shadow</em>, <em>improved shadow</em>, or <em>greater shadow</em> armor special ability, the miss chance increases to 50%.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>shadow walk</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus</p>",
